title: Match of the Day - 6th December 2014 - HDTV X264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD     
Date: Saturday 6th December 2014 
Time: 22:20 to 23:45 

Gary Lineker presents highlights of the day's seven Premier League games, including Chelsea's trip to Newcastle as the Londoners look to keep their title bid on course. Chelsea have never won at St James' Park in the league under Jose Mourinho, and their previous two visits have ended in defeat. Elsewhere, Arsenal take on a Stoke team who have a fantastic record over Arsene Wenger's side at the Britannia Stadium, with just one defeat in the Premier League. Plus a London derby between Tottenham and Crystal Palace, while the champions Manchester City host Everton in the evening kick-off. Early-season strugglers QPR and Burnley meet at Loftus Road, Hull are at home to West Brom and Liverpool host Sunderland. The studio experts are Alan Shears and Ruud Gullit
